cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision and image processing techniques for cross-view matching, which falls under the scope of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the use of GIS (geographic information system) data, which falls under the scope of computer graphics (cs.GR). The proposed method involves the use of semantic information and machine learning techniques, which falls under the scope of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves the evaluation of the proposed method on challenging query images, which falls under the scope of multimedia (cs.MM).
